\newlabel{fig:fig5}{{4}{11}{Aggregation Function Comparison. Ablation study comparing min, mean, median, and XOR aggregation functions. XOR achieves lowest MSE (0.1452 at position 16) but does not preserve MinHash property. Min is the only function that preserves Pr[match]=J while achieving reasonable accuracy}{figure.4}{}}
